<h2 id="wasd-introduces-wrist-rest">WASD Introduces Wrist Rest</h2>
<p>This is not a revolutionary development as many people now seem to be producing wrist rests. The current options are for  tenkeyless and a full sized wooden wrist rest. Priced at $58 and $60.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.wasdkeyboards.com/index.php/products/keyboard-accessories/14-wenge-hardwood-wrist-rest.html">Tenkeyless</a></li>
