<h2 id="massdrop">Massdrop</h2>
<p>Massdrop has done a couple of surprising things in the past week.</p>

<h3 id="realforce-hi-pro-and-fountain-pen-bundle">Realforce Hi-Pro and Fountain Pen Bundle</h3>
<p>For all the people who were thinking about buying a Hi-Pro and were also in the market for a fountain pen. Massdrop now has you covered with this bundle. It seems like a strange choice for a bundle and I really canâ€™t see the reason behind it.</p>

